    <h2 class="section--heading">Overview</h2>
    <p class="section--body">I’m a Front-end Designer at <a href="http://www.nbcuni.com/digital/nbc-news-digital/" title="NBC News Digital" target="_blank" rel="external">NBC News Digital</a>. I take pride in designing and building clean, accessible, creative interactive media. I get pumped about CSS, HTML, typography, mobile development, responsive web design, and the idea that people use the things that I create. Before NBC News I worked in New Orleans at the design studio <a href="http://thinkabig.com/" title="Thinka" target="_blank" rel="external">Thinka</a> and before that the ad agency <a href="http://z-comm.com/" title="z-comm.com" target="_blank" rel="external">Zehnder Communications</a>. I’m also the creator of <a href="http://typesettings.io/" title="typesettings.io" target="_blank" rel="external">Typesettings</a> and <a href="https://github.com/ianrose/gridsettings" title="GitHub" target="_blank" rel="external">Gridsettings</a>.</p>
