  <div class="row">
    <h2 class="section--heading">Colophon</h2>
    <p class="section--body">This site is built with <a href="http://hexo.io/" title="hexo.io" target="_blank" rel="external">Hexo</a>, <a href="http://sass-lang.com/" title="Sass-lang.com" target="_blank" rel="external">Sass</a>, <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/CSS/Flexible_boxes" title="MDN" target="_blank" rel="external">CSS Flexbox</a> and hosted on <a href="https://github.com/ianrose/ianrose.github.io" title="GitHub Repo" target="_blank" rel="external">GitHub</a>. The body text is set in <a href="http://www.fonts.com/font/dstype-foundry/leitura-news?isRatingExpanded=False" title="fonts.com" target="_blank" rel="external">Leitura News</a>. Supplmentary text is set in <a href="http://www.fonts.com/font/dstype-foundry/leitura/display-roman" title="fonts.com" target="_blank" rel="external">Leitura Display</a>. The headings are set in <a href="http://www.fonts.com/font/linotype/neue-haas-grotesk#product_top" title="fonts.com" target="_blank" rel="external">Neue Haas Grotesk Display</a> while the UI elements are in <a href="http://www.fonts.com/font/linotype/neue-haas-grotesk#product_top" title="fonts.com" target="_blank" rel="external">Neue Haas Grotesk</a>. All the fonts are served by <a href="http://www.fonts.com/" title="Fonts.com" target="_blank" rel="external">fonts.com</a> and the CDN is provided by <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/" title="cloudflare.com" target="_blank" rel="external">CloudFlare</a>. Also, thanks to <a href="http://bradoyler.com" title="bradoyler.com" target="_blank" rel="external">Brad Oyler</a> for all his help.</p>
